7. violation_description: a brief description of the violation

17. address: the address of the property being inspected
18. street_number: the street number of the property
19. street_direction: the direction of the street (N, S, E, W, etc.)
20. street_name: the name of the street
21. street_type: the type of street (AVE, ST, etc.)
22. property_group: the group or category of the property
23. ssa: the SSA (Social Security Administration) code for the property
24. latitude: the latitude coordinate of the property
25. longitude: the longitude coordinate of the property
26. location: the location of the property (a pair of latitude and longitude coordinates)

These features provide a comprehensive description of each instance, including the details of the violation, the inspection, and the property being inspected.
